D15 1320  5    recluse united with divine essence. But this esoteric
D15 1330  3    doctrine was lost in the shuffle to acquire special
D15 1330 12    powers. The anchorite strove, in fact, to magically
D15 1340  8    influence the world of spirits in the same way that
D15 1350  8    the divine emperor manifested his power. Thus, the
D15 1360  3    Mahayana metaphysic of mystical union for salvation
D15 1360 10    was distilled down to a bare self-seeking, and for
