D15 1390  3    as soon as an early Zen master attained fame in seclusion,
D15 1400  2    he was called out into the world to exercise his powers.
D15 1410  1    The early anchorite masters attracted disciples because
D15 1410  8    of their presumed ability to perform miracles.
